/*============================================================

Challenge 01

Title:
Canadian Customers for a Marketing Campaign

Department:
Marketing

Difficulty:
⭐⭐⭐ Intermediate

Business Request:
The Marketing department is preparing a campaign targeted
exclusively at customers living in Canada.

Required Information:
- Customer ID
- First Name
- Last Name
- Email
- Country

Requirements:
- Include only customers living in Canada.
- Sort the results alphabetically by last name and,
  if two customers share the same last name,
  by first name.

Skills Demonstrated:
- INNER JOIN
- WHERE
- ORDER BY
- Multi-table relationships

Concepts Learned:
- Navigating related tables
- Filtering by information stored in another table
- Translating business requirements into SQL

Database:
MySQL - Sakila

============================================================*/

SELECT
    customer.customer_id,
    customer.first_name,
    customer.last_name,
    customer.email,
    country.country
FROM customer
INNER JOIN address
    ON customer.address_id = address.address_id
INNER JOIN city
    ON address.city_id = city.city_id
INNER JOIN country
    ON city.country_id = country.country_id
WHERE country.country = 'Canada'
ORDER BY
    customer.last_name,
    customer.first_name;

/*
============================================================

Business Insight

This query helps the Marketing team identify all customers
living in Canada, making it possible to launch regional
campaigns and personalized communications.

============================================================
*/
